summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2010 CARGO PRO C 6.5. THE CONTACT STATED THAT CRACKS HAD DEVELOPED IN THE FRONT OF THE ALUMINUM FRAME BEHIND THE COUPLER. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT TAKEN TO A DEALER.
